snippet.title: Power Hover: Cruise Trailer
snippet.description:
Power Hover:Cruise! Hover your way in the randomly generated underground tunnels filled with danger or take to the skies and do crazy loops above the clouds! Survive as long as you can. Unlock gallery items and new robot riders with different skills to help you on your way! 

Coming out 10th of August 2017 for iOS Appstore, for Free!
